assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Sun Messe Co., Ltd. operates as a communication service center for printing, publishing, digital media, videos, and events businesses in Japan. It provides various commercial, publishing, package, and form printing products. The company also offers promotion solutions, such as catalogue promotion support, image database, manuscript submission, 3D computer graphics, inventory management, shipping agency, flyer production support system, digital flyer, POP advertising entry, and area marketing systems. In addition, it provides digital press services, including information processing, print on demand, continuous paper digital press, multi binding, automatic encapsulation and sealing, final inspection function, one-to-one printing, and original envelop processing services; and 3D package design and package CAD data creation systems, as well as sample cutters, in-store promotion, UV printers, Thomson machine, and box making machines. Further, the company offers support in the areas of website operation, social media, iBooks and eBook, digital signage, video content creation, augmented reality, application development, access analysis, membership management, and web promotion. Additionally, it provides silkscreen printing, clean assembly, noricle, UV printing, center lip system, remote calibration system, printed electronics; carbon management; events and conventions; ecommunication; and universal design. Sun Messe Co., Ltd. was founded in 1935 and is headquartered in Ogaki, Japan.
